{"tid":371752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫老豆上位嗰個「揀錯歌」照殺入《全美》準決賽","createTime":"2017-08-24T01:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T11:14:42.000Z","uid":7775,"like":2,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7cf5c26ca8788600ba9a950c1b4c9f349162014","tid":371752,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:02:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170824/bkn-20170824084137679-0824_00862_001.html/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170824%2Fbkn-20170824084137679-0824_00862_001.html%2F&d=ZXwma8W0dXeta1FKeUUtbzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=2d6a1b53\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170824/bkn-20170824084137679-0824_00862_001.html/</a><br />\n<br />\n9歲「香港小巨肺」譚芷昀（Celine）越洋挑戰美國才藝真人騷《全美一叮》（America's Got Talent，AGT），特別在本月14日已出發飛往美國積極備戰，希望可以殺入準決賽。雖然昨日被評判Mel B批評揀錯歌，但最終不負眾望成功晉級！剛於美國播映的最新一集中，Celine憑演唱天后瑪莉亞卡里（Mariah Carey）與已故天后雲妮侯斯頓（Whitney Houston）合唱的電影《埃及王子》（The Prince of Egypt）主題曲《When You Believe》出戰成功入圍，再下一城與最強對手的10歲「小Whitney Houston（小雲妮）」Angelica Hale交手，冠軍在望，再一次為港人爭光！"},{"pid":"8d7d182870c13b3cbeace0583c932fb00ffaae70","tid":371752,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da99a02d06c1545a0db82b60892d27de70e55601","tid":371752,"uid":75365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"快撚啲 Out咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c659920497efe2e44cba7656db2b4b7121fc3a1","tid":371752,"uid":12449,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"驚俾人投訴種族歧視？"},{"pid":"93137aa1841ad35e34b503919d547868464c9581","tid":371752,"uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:18:22.000Z","msg":"唱歌機器<br />\n得個唱字 無感情 唔覺意好聽<br />\n反正蘿莉細路女一行